---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { showBuyAudiobookButton, showAmazonTag, book } from "../config.json";
---

<main
  class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 mb-8 mt-12 sm:mt-12 sm:mb-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-32 md:mb-20 xl:mt-23 xl:mb-24"
>
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
    <div class="mb-12 md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
      {
        showAmazonTag && (
          <div class="text-base uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">
            <Image
              class="inline h-5 relative"
              style="top:3px"
              src="/amazon.svg"
              alt="amazon.com"
              width={300}
              height={480}
              loading={"eager"}
            />{" "}
            best-seller
          </div>
        )
      }

      <h1
        class="mt-1 text-4xl tracking-tight leading-10 font-extrabold font-serif text-gray-900 sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        One Plus One<br class="hidden md:inline" /><span class="underline"
          >is One</span
        >
      </h1><p
        class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-700 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl font-body"
      >
        A deep dive into the intersection between science and spirituality
      </p><p
        class="p-5 mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-2xl font-body"
      >
        “The totality of knowledge about the universe is sealed and encrypted in
        the initial Singularity, which threatens vanishing physics from its own
        recognition, as if it had reached the horizon of a black hole”.
      </p>
      <p
        class="p-5 mt-3 text-base text-gray-500 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-2xl font-body"
      >
        “I want to know how God created this world. I’m not interested in this
        or that phenomenon, in the spectrum of this or that element. I want to
        know His thoughts; the rest are just details.” <strong>Einstein</strong>
      </p>
      <div>
        <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <div>
            <a
              href="/public/chapter-4.pdf"
              target="_blank"
              class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 rounded-md font-semibold text-black bg-book-theme hover:bg-yellow-200 focus:outline-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
              >Read a sample chapter</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><div
      class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-4 lg:flex lg:items-center"
    >
      <a class="book-container" href="#ebook"
        ><div class="book">
          <Image
            src={"/cover-2.jpeg"}
            width={300}
            height={600}
            alt={book.title}
            format={"avif"}
            loading={"eager"}
          />
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
